</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nt">&lt;ul</span> <span class="na">id=</span><span class="s">&quot;categories&quot;</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>  <span class="nt">&lt;li&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>    <span class="nt">&lt;em&gt;</span>2<span class="nt">&lt;/em&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>    <span class="nt">&lt;a</span> <span class="na">href=</span><span class="s">&quot;http://brousalis.com/blog/categories/personal&quot;</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>personal<span class="nt">&lt;/a&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>    <span class="nt">&lt;span</span> <span class="na">style=</span><span class="s">&quot;width:50%&quot;</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>bar<span class="nt">&lt;/span&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>    <span class="nt">&lt;div</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">&quot;personal&quot;</span><span class="nt">&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>  <span class="nt">&lt;/li&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nt">&lt;/ul&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nt">&lt;p&gt;</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div></p>

<p>The <em>div</em> is the icon, optional, and the width % is calculated by the post count of the category divided by the total post count.</p>

